A. Broadcast address
B. Multicast
C. DNS
D. TCP

SYN flood causes server to:
A. Complete handshake
B. Keep half-open connections
C. Encrypt traffic
D. Drop packets

Botnets are controlled using:
A. IDS
B. Command and Control (C2)
C. Firewalls
D. Antivirus

