A. SYN flood
B. Smurf
C. SQL Injection
D. UDP flood

Session hijacking is easier when:
A. HTTPS is used
B. Session IDs are predictable
C. Cookies are secure
D. MFA enabled

Types of session hijacking include:
A. Active and passive
B. Physical and logical
C. Internal and external
D. Wired and wireless

