A. Listening only
B. Taking over session
C. Logging traffic
D. Packet filtering

Botnets are commonly used for:
A. Data backup
B. DDoS attacks
C. Encryption
D. Authentication

SYN cookies help prevent:
A. DNS attacks
B. SYN flood
C. ARP poisoning
D. Sniffing

Session hijacking mainly violates:
A. Availability
B. Integrity
C. Confidentiality
D. Authentication

